## AI Models
Haiku (claude-haiku-4-5-20251001): image capture, search, assistant preview
Sonnet (dynamic latest, fallback claude-sonnet-4-6): AI assistant

## API Routes
POST /api/capture — Haiku vision → contacts/deals/tasks JSON
POST /api/assistant — Sonnet + 9 tools, agentic loop, logs events after write
POST /api/assistant/preview — Haiku confirm card before write actions
POST /api/search — Haiku intent parsing + Supabase queries
POST /api/nudges — proactive home screen cards
POST /api/tasks — create task
PATCH /api/tasks/[id] — update task (status, title, due_date, priority)

## Assistant Tools (9)
add_contact, find_contact, add_company, add_deal, add_task, search_crm, get_pipeline_summary, update_deal_stage, update_deal_financials

## Database Tables
users, organisations, organisation_members, subscriptions
companies, contacts, deals, deal_contacts, events, tasks

## Schema Notes
contacts: full_name (not first/last), role (not title)
organisation_members: org_id (not organisation_id), role: admin/manager/rep
deals stages: lead → qualified → demo → proposal → negotiation → closed_won → closed_lost
deals fields: confirmed_revenue, invoice_ref, po_ref, invoice_date, po_date, payment_status (none/invoiced/paid)
tasks fields: title, status, done (bool), due_date, priority, deal_id, contact_id, user_id
events: jsonb metadata, every capture and assistant write action logged

## Key DB Functions
create_organisation(name, slug) — creates org + admin member + free subscription
get_user_org_id() — returns current user's org
RLS: rep=own data, manager=read org, admin=full org
Server components use service role key, client uses anon key

## Auth Flow
/login → magic link / Google / GitHub OAuth → /auth/callback → has org? redirect / : redirect /onboarding
Onboarding: create workspace (admin) or join existing

## Layout Architecture
Mobile (<768px): bottom nav fixed (Home | Capture pulse button | Tracking), content pb-[90px]
Desktop (≥768px): sidebar fixed left 210px, content md:ml-[210px], no bottom nav
layout.tsx wrapper div: px-4 py-4 pb-[90px] md:px-10 md:py-8 md:pb-8 md:max-w-[1240px] md:mx-auto
Nav hidden on /login /onboarding /auth/* via NavVisibilityWrapper
useIsDesktop() hook (768px breakpoint) used across all client components

